WEBVTT

01:35.900 --> 01:40.980
=Love Beyond the Grave=
(Adapted from the novel by Li Qingran)

01:41.260 --> 01:43.980
=Episode 6=

01:46.550 --> 01:47.580
- Kill her!
- Kill her!

01:48.060 --> 01:48.910
You people are

01:48.910 --> 01:50.750
high and mighty.

01:51.420 --> 01:52.910
You want me to die?

01:54.060 --> 01:55.060
If I have to die,

01:55.700 --> 01:57.270
we'll die together!

02:27.300 --> 02:29.550
(If you die with evil obsessions,)

02:30.460 --> 02:32.460
(evil spirits will come
and plague the world.)

02:34.550 --> 02:35.390
Who is this girl?

02:35.510 --> 02:36.350
I don't know.

03:00.700 --> 03:01.540
I...

03:08.180 --> 03:09.020
My town, Liangzhou,

03:09.620 --> 03:10.830
was ravaged by Chong troops.

03:12.350 --> 03:13.350
My fellow countrymen

03:13.350 --> 03:14.420
were killed by them.

03:15.620 --> 03:17.390
Just now, I heard her wild remarks,

03:17.740 --> 03:18.950
and anger overwhelmed me.

03:20.420 --> 03:22.460
So, I was dying to kill her.

03:24.270 --> 03:25.110
I...

03:39.140 --> 03:40.580
Don't draw my sword casually.

03:44.020 --> 03:45.460
Please don't blame me, General.

03:51.420 --> 03:52.990
You contributed a lot to my army.

03:54.420 --> 03:55.390
Sadness overwhelmed you,

03:55.390 --> 03:56.230
and you killed her.

03:57.580 --> 03:58.700
I will not blame you.

03:59.270 --> 04:00.950
Bravo! Well done!

04:00.950 --> 04:07.070
- Well done!
- You did great!

04:12.180 --> 04:13.020
Miss He,

04:13.700 --> 04:14.550
she hasn't confessed

04:14.550 --> 04:15.900
how she sneaked into the granary.

04:15.900 --> 04:16.740
You...

04:16.740 --> 04:17.990
How could you just kill her?

04:19.150 --> 04:19.990
Mr. Lin,

04:21.350 --> 04:22.550
we can still interrogate

04:22.550 --> 04:23.390
the guards on duty.

04:23.910 --> 04:24.860
Not too much was burned.

04:25.350 --> 04:26.190
It's all right.

04:28.080 --> 04:28.940
Put out promptly,

04:29.060 --> 04:30.260
the fire didn't burn much.

04:30.930 --> 04:31.770
That's great!

04:31.770 --> 04:32.940
Everybody, don't panic.

04:34.300 --> 04:35.940
Later, we'll distribute food.

04:36.180 --> 04:37.150
Distribute food?

04:37.300 --> 04:38.150
So, we really didn't

04:38.150 --> 04:39.300
lose too much.

04:40.260 --> 04:41.420
Everybody, disperse.

04:42.030 --> 04:42.910
Move, everybody.

04:42.910 --> 04:43.990
Everybody, go home.

04:43.990 --> 04:44.940
Break it up.

04:45.300 --> 04:46.140
Don't worry.

04:46.520 --> 04:47.470
We will distribute food

04:47.470 --> 04:48.420
as scheduled.

04:49.670 --> 04:50.740
- Go home.
- Go.

04:50.860 --> 04:51.700
Break it up.

04:55.860 --> 04:56.790
Why did you do that?

05:00.030 --> 05:01.420
If He Yan had died like that,

05:01.670 --> 05:02.740
evil spirits would prey.

05:03.940 --> 05:05.380
Just pretend I was being nosy.

05:09.790 --> 05:10.630
General Duan,

05:11.940 --> 05:13.300
how on earth

05:14.500 --> 05:15.820
did you get this sword?

05:16.860 --> 05:18.260
That's a long story.

05:19.350 --> 05:20.790
One day, on a bridge of Nandu,

05:21.550 --> 05:22.590
I met an old man.

05:25.710 --> 05:26.740
This is the truth.

05:27.860 --> 05:28.910
Not long before I left,

05:29.420 --> 05:30.420
I met a strange old man

05:30.420 --> 05:31.260
on that bridge.

05:31.790 --> 05:33.230
He said he was hundreds of years old.

05:34.470 --> 05:35.380
He suddenly stopped me

05:35.790 --> 05:36.740
and gave me this sword.

05:37.470 --> 05:38.310
He also told me

05:38.420 --> 05:39.500
it was the Deliverance.

05:40.260 --> 05:41.420
It means dispelling illusions

05:42.230 --> 05:43.420
and resentments of mortals.

05:43.990 --> 05:44.990
Those struck by it

05:45.420 --> 05:46.500
will get rid of illusions.

05:49.820 --> 05:50.790
That's so you, Miss He.

05:52.300 --> 05:53.230
You know everything.

06:01.590 --> 06:02.430
I'll go investigate

06:02.440 --> 06:03.500
the fire case.

06:03.740 --> 06:04.580
I'll take my leave.

06:05.820 --> 06:06.660
General Duan,

06:08.740 --> 06:10.350
you see how oddly I behave.

06:11.060 --> 06:12.260
Don't you suspect

06:12.500 --> 06:13.350
that I was sent

06:13.350 --> 06:15.060
by Duke Pei or North Chong?

06:15.550 --> 06:17.300
Do you just take orders from people?

06:18.300 --> 06:19.350
Judging from your skull,

06:20.060 --> 06:21.500
you're born unruly

06:22.380 --> 06:23.740
and you act on your own authority.

06:31.620 --> 06:32.460
(Did he)

06:32.670 --> 06:34.230
(get the Deliverance)

06:34.740 --> 06:36.150
(because he was my spell bearer?)

06:42.300 --> 06:43.140
What's up?

06:43.420 --> 06:44.260
Great Ancestor,

06:44.380 --> 06:46.060
I found the real Duan Xu!

06:46.260 --> 06:47.120
How did you?

06:47.150 --> 06:48.260
I found Du Zheng,

06:48.260 --> 06:49.860
who served Duan Xu in Daizhou.

06:50.150 --> 06:51.150
He gave me a portrait

06:51.150 --> 06:52.060
of the young master

06:52.060 --> 06:53.380
he had served.

06:57.110 --> 06:59.500
Fang Xianye, the Censorial Counselor.

06:59.940 --> 07:02.380
He's the real Duan Xu.

07:03.660 --> 07:05.980
(Fang Xianye, Censorial Counselor)

07:05.990 --> 07:06.830
Your Majesty,

07:07.470 --> 07:08.310
there's no way.

07:10.110 --> 07:12.820
Can we really not
deliver supplies to Shuozhou

07:14.030 --> 07:16.740
without suffering

07:17.550 --> 07:19.790
(Emperor of Great Liang)
any casualties?

07:22.380 --> 07:23.220
Your Majesty.

07:23.220 --> 07:24.150
(Yao Jianhe, Duke Pei)

07:24.150 --> 07:25.820
Although Duan Xu has occupied Shuozhou,

07:26.550 --> 07:28.300
(Du Yanting, Chancellor)
he disobeyed orders

07:28.590 --> 07:29.470
and defied the law.

07:29.740 --> 07:30.790
(Duan Chengzhang, Minister of Rites)
He sent troops

07:30.790 --> 07:31.790
without telling anyone.

07:32.260 --> 07:34.550
So his army has been trapped

07:34.910 --> 07:35.860
in Shuozhou.

07:36.150 --> 07:36.990
Now,

07:37.110 --> 07:38.420
even 200,000 Hulan soldiers

07:38.420 --> 07:39.260
are lurking greedily.

07:39.550 --> 07:40.470
How can the supplies

07:41.260 --> 07:43.300
be delivered to Shuozhou?

07:43.740 --> 07:45.110
Are you saying

07:45.260 --> 07:47.420
we're going to abandon

07:47.420 --> 07:49.380
twenty thousand soldiers

07:49.380 --> 07:50.260
and the citizens?

07:50.260 --> 07:51.100
How can we help?

07:51.790 --> 07:53.030
Duan Xu's life matters.

07:53.620 --> 07:55.260
What about the lives

07:55.260 --> 07:56.790
- of other soldiers?
- You...

07:56.790 --> 07:57.630
Enough.

07:59.990 --> 08:02.230
North Chong has occupied
the north of the Guanhe River

08:02.230 --> 08:03.070
for thirty years.

08:03.590 --> 08:05.500
Now, we're about to cross the river.

08:05.710 --> 08:07.590
We can't just abandon Shuozhou.

08:07.910 --> 08:08.750
However,

08:08.760 --> 08:10.740
what General Duan's doing
is extremely perilous.

08:10.910 --> 08:12.820
Duke Pei's concern is justified.

08:14.060 --> 08:14.900
Your Majesty,

08:15.150 --> 08:16.260
Shuozhou is under siege.

08:16.470 --> 08:17.740
Supplies will run short.

08:17.990 --> 08:19.230
Even if there's a slim chance,

08:19.500 --> 08:20.670
we can't give in.

08:20.910 --> 08:22.420
We understand that Minister Duan

08:22.420 --> 08:23.260
cares for his son.

08:23.620 --> 08:24.460
But now,

08:24.590 --> 08:25.910
no one can fight his way

08:25.910 --> 08:27.300
through 200,000 Hulan soldiers.

08:27.910 --> 08:28.910
We can gather supplies

08:29.060 --> 08:30.470
before we manage to deliver them.

08:30.990 --> 08:31.830
Who will

08:32.620 --> 08:33.590
take this mission?

08:36.500 --> 08:37.340
Me.

08:37.380 --> 08:38.310
I'll take this mission.

08:41.500 --> 08:43.470
The court is dismissed!

08:51.500 --> 08:53.430
You got my son exiled to the front.

08:54.380 --> 08:55.900
And now, you want to get him killed.

09:05.580 --> 09:07.340
(Chongde Chamber)

09:07.350 --> 09:08.430
He Yan got the key

09:08.430 --> 09:09.710
to the granary from Xie.

09:10.190 --> 09:11.430
Obviously, she knew

09:11.740 --> 09:13.710
the Lins guarded the granary with us.

09:14.430 --> 09:15.350
She also knew very well

09:15.350 --> 09:16.990
about the patrols and shifts.

09:17.590 --> 09:18.430
Captain Han,

09:18.740 --> 09:20.260
you're in charge of granary defense.

09:20.830 --> 09:21.670
You must find out

09:22.190 --> 09:23.030
what happened today.

09:23.070 --> 09:23.910
Yes.

09:27.310 --> 09:28.150
General Duan.

09:28.480 --> 09:29.330
General Duan,

09:29.350 --> 09:30.500
I ask for your fair judgment.

09:30.500 --> 09:31.380
General Duan!

09:31.740 --> 09:32.990
I'm afraid someone else

09:33.310 --> 09:34.620
is behind Xie.

09:35.110 --> 09:36.350
Compared to finding the spy,

09:37.140 --> 09:38.950
we have something more urgent to do.

09:41.860 --> 09:43.140
I've blocked the news.

09:44.380 --> 09:45.470
But I want to be honest

09:45.990 --> 09:46.950
with you all.

09:47.900 --> 09:49.230
The supplies from Marshal Qin

09:49.950 --> 09:50.950
would have been enough

09:50.950 --> 09:51.900
for fifteen days.

09:53.140 --> 09:54.710
But they've been burned to ashes.

09:55.710 --> 09:57.190
All we have now is some food

09:57.380 --> 09:58.780
Mr. Lin has collected for me.

10:00.070 --> 10:01.590
Far from enough, though.

10:03.470 --> 10:04.780
That madwoman...

10:05.540 --> 10:06.740
What a mess!

10:07.380 --> 10:08.310
Oh, it's burning me.

10:10.500 --> 10:12.380
General, why don't we fight our way out

10:12.780 --> 10:14.310
and die together with Chong soldiers?

10:14.950 --> 10:15.990
The more I kill,

10:15.990 --> 10:16.830
the more it's worth.

10:18.950 --> 10:20.470
It's not time for death yet.

10:21.740 --> 10:22.860
Before the enemy arrived,

10:23.140 --> 10:24.710
I had asked my men to scout this area.

10:25.380 --> 10:26.430
There's a secret path

10:26.900 --> 10:28.140
on the sunny side of Mount Peng.

10:29.380 --> 10:30.230
Tall enough for horses

10:31.350 --> 10:32.740
and wide enough for five men.

10:33.590 --> 10:34.780
It leads to the enemy's rear.

10:35.780 --> 10:37.470
As people say, tit for tat is only fair.

10:38.350 --> 10:39.500
They burned our supplies

10:40.620 --> 10:42.310
and we'll take theirs

10:42.740 --> 10:43.590
in appreciation.

10:44.260 --> 10:45.900
If Chong soldiers deliver supplies,

10:46.540 --> 10:47.470
they have to pass

10:47.470 --> 10:48.540
through northern cities.

10:49.620 --> 10:51.380
I have relatives there, too.

10:52.110 --> 10:53.350
I'll contact them by pigeons,

10:54.020 --> 10:55.470
asking them to watch the grain carts.

10:56.070 --> 10:56.910
Then let's do it.

11:18.060 --> 11:20.580
(The Collection of Military Techniques)

11:26.430 --> 11:27.540
(Duan Xu)
(You're a fake.)

11:28.190 --> 11:29.780
(You aren't an imperial relative.)

11:30.190 --> 11:31.350
(You may even be a Chong.)

11:32.710 --> 11:34.260
(Why did you fight aggressively)

11:34.260 --> 11:35.100
(for Great Liang)

11:35.470 --> 11:36.950
(and kill Chong troops with zeal?)

11:37.140 --> 11:38.190
(Duan Xu,)

11:38.190 --> 11:39.660
(what exactly are you up to?)

11:47.900 --> 11:48.740
General.

11:50.430 --> 11:51.270
What's up?

11:55.020 --> 11:55.950
You ordered me to solve

11:55.950 --> 11:56.900
the fire case.

11:58.500 --> 11:59.780
But I'm confused about something.

12:00.660 --> 12:01.620
I seek your guidance.

12:02.020 --> 12:02.860
Go ahead.

12:03.020 --> 12:04.620
Why are you so familiar with North Chong

12:05.260 --> 12:07.020
when you've never been in the army?

12:10.370 --> 12:11.230
Are you suspecting

12:11.230 --> 12:12.430
I have a connection with them?

12:13.350 --> 12:14.190
Yes.

12:19.950 --> 12:21.380
I asked you to find the spy.

12:22.170 --> 12:23.020
But you suspect me

12:23.020 --> 12:24.260
in the first place.

12:25.950 --> 12:27.590
Are you worried I'm colluding with them

12:29.190 --> 12:30.110
and just pretending?

12:31.540 --> 12:32.380
I'm not sure.

12:33.230 --> 12:34.230
Please explain.

12:40.230 --> 12:41.540
Captain Han, I heard

12:43.140 --> 12:44.540
you escaped from North Chong.

12:47.110 --> 12:48.350
You must have more connections

12:49.470 --> 12:50.740
with them.

12:53.430 --> 12:54.660
I don't remember what happened

12:56.020 --> 12:56.990
back there.

13:08.590 --> 13:09.900
You can't answer me,

13:11.350 --> 13:12.710
but seek my answer instead.

13:13.590 --> 13:15.020
If I suppose

13:16.470 --> 13:17.860
an unidentified man like you

13:19.140 --> 13:19.980
from North Chong

13:20.230 --> 13:21.350
might be a spy,

13:22.500 --> 13:23.990
how can you refute that?

13:29.620 --> 13:31.260
You have the guts to suspect me.

13:33.110 --> 13:33.950
Captain Han,

13:35.260 --> 13:36.860
I'll pretend I didn't hear this.

13:37.830 --> 13:38.670
Don't worry.

13:40.070 --> 13:41.780
If Shuozhou is captured,

13:44.110 --> 13:45.260
I will not survive alone.

14:38.470 --> 14:39.540
(He has acute senses)

14:40.620 --> 14:42.230
(and remarkable responsiveness.)

14:43.590 --> 14:45.310
(He's indeed the best among mortals.)

14:46.500 --> 14:47.660
(I think it will feel great)

14:47.660 --> 14:48.900
(when I borrow his five senses.)

14:58.860 --> 15:00.190
(Look at this young general.)

15:00.950 --> 15:02.780
(What did he suffer in his childhood?)

15:05.020 --> 15:06.740
(What lies beneath the scars)

15:07.470 --> 15:08.740
(of the branding iron?)

15:09.780 --> 15:12.430
(And how are they related
to his identity?)

17:06.540 --> 17:07.740
Excellent senses.

17:09.990 --> 17:10.950
Foxy,

17:12.100 --> 17:13.300
you're qualified

17:13.870 --> 17:14.870
to be my spell bearer.

17:39.060 --> 17:41.140
(Liang)

18:06.150 --> 18:08.260
General, you're still young.

18:08.630 --> 18:09.740
In face of a major mission,

18:10.060 --> 18:11.540
you were also too scared to sleep.

18:12.470 --> 18:13.500
Don't worry.

18:13.950 --> 18:14.990
Today, I will

18:14.990 --> 18:15.830
scout ahead for you.

18:16.190 --> 18:17.340
You'll be safe.

18:18.540 --> 18:19.780
Pass the order. Call up troops.

18:20.260 --> 18:21.100
Commandant Wu.

18:23.150 --> 18:24.260
You should stay in Shuozhou.

18:26.630 --> 18:27.470
What do you mean?

18:28.910 --> 18:30.430
You don't trust me?

18:31.100 --> 18:32.020
If I can't come back,

18:32.950 --> 18:34.430
you will command in town.

18:35.230 --> 18:36.150
My army trusts you.

18:37.300 --> 18:38.140
I trust you, too.

18:40.430 --> 18:41.300
I wrote to Marshal Qin

18:41.300 --> 18:42.540
about the situation in town.

18:43.020 --> 18:44.430
If tensions in Yuzhou ease,

18:44.780 --> 18:46.300
he'll try to send reinforcements.

18:47.300 --> 18:49.340
Then why don't you stay here?

18:49.580 --> 18:51.150
We can go intercept the supplies.

18:52.780 --> 18:53.870
If the mission fails

18:54.150 --> 18:55.230
and I'm still in town,

18:55.740 --> 18:57.190
will Marshal Qin still rescue us?

18:57.850 --> 18:58.690
But...

18:58.710 --> 18:59.550
We...

18:59.780 --> 19:00.620
Han Lingqiu.

19:01.780 --> 19:02.620
Here.

19:03.060 --> 19:04.060
Get 800 elite soldiers.

19:04.540 --> 19:05.380
In the mid-afternoon,

19:05.630 --> 19:06.470
we'll depart.

19:06.670 --> 19:07.510
Yes.

19:12.060 --> 19:13.710
We serve the same country.

19:13.910 --> 19:15.230
How come Marshal Qin

19:15.230 --> 19:16.070
will not rescue us?

19:16.540 --> 19:17.380
Commandant Wu,

19:18.230 --> 19:19.070
take my advice.

19:19.350 --> 19:20.190
With your temper,

19:20.200 --> 19:21.390
do not try to be an official.

19:21.740 --> 19:22.820
The court, right now,

19:23.060 --> 19:24.060
is in dire straits.

19:24.500 --> 19:25.780
Or you'll be in deep trouble.

19:28.470 --> 19:29.310
Meng Wan, Qingsheng.

19:30.430 --> 19:31.580
You must help Commandant Wu

19:32.190 --> 19:33.030
defend Shuozhou.

19:33.740 --> 19:34.580
- Yes.
- Yes.

19:42.220 --> 19:43.260
Darn it.

19:43.870 --> 19:44.740
Why do I feel

19:44.740 --> 19:46.540
this guy is protecting me?

20:00.300 --> 20:01.390
Foxy.

21:08.210 --> 21:09.100
Take cover!

21:09.100 --> 21:10.040
Hide!

21:19.820 --> 21:21.670
Ambush! Take cover!

21:22.230 --> 21:23.070
Captain Han.

21:23.110 --> 21:23.970
Don't stop.

21:24.060 --> 21:24.910
Go kill the enemies.

21:47.660 --> 21:48.520
Great.

21:48.540 --> 21:49.390
It really is grain.

21:49.990 --> 21:51.740
General Duan is truly prophetic.

21:52.230 --> 21:53.070
Move, move.

22:07.870 --> 22:08.710
Ambush!

22:08.920 --> 22:09.770
Hide now!

22:09.780 --> 22:11.100
Take cover!

22:11.340 --> 22:12.230
Hide!

22:14.190 --> 22:15.030
Hide!

22:29.670 --> 22:31.060
So, someone is watching behind us

22:31.500 --> 22:32.630
to hunt us.

22:33.230 --> 22:34.300
We're ambushed.

22:39.340 --> 22:40.870
I think they'll take you and me alive.

22:46.950 --> 22:47.870
Prepare to fight!

24:22.060 --> 24:23.540
As a spirit,

24:23.990 --> 24:25.500
I didn't want to get involved.

24:26.830 --> 24:27.710
But just now,

24:27.720 --> 24:29.560
I made a deal with the young man

24:29.570 --> 24:30.750
you shot to death.

24:31.870 --> 24:33.950
He begged me to save Liang soldiers,

24:35.060 --> 24:36.150
and I agreed.

24:37.900 --> 24:38.740
She'll save us.

24:38.740 --> 24:40.380
- She'll save us.
- Great.

24:40.400 --> 24:42.150
So, North Chong soldiers,

24:43.020 --> 24:43.990
will you do this

24:43.990 --> 24:45.060
for my sake?

24:45.910 --> 24:47.230
Let them go.

24:49.260 --> 24:50.100
He Xiaoxiao,

24:51.300 --> 24:52.140
stop pretending.

25:04.430 --> 25:06.190
Who would dare to bully you?

25:07.340 --> 25:08.820
Foxy,

25:08.950 --> 25:10.390
you made an unexpected mistake, too.

25:10.390 --> 25:12.100
Stop being mysterious!

25:12.100 --> 25:12.950
Kill!

25:12.960 --> 25:13.950
Kill!

25:22.710 --> 25:24.060
Do you really think

25:24.230 --> 25:25.740
I'm asking for your permission?

25:42.470 --> 25:43.540
Move!

25:46.100 --> 25:46.940
Run!

26:31.020 --> 26:31.860
Rest in peace.

26:47.390 --> 26:48.230
Miss He,

26:49.950 --> 26:50.790
wipe off the blood.

27:00.500 --> 27:01.500
And then?

27:05.230 --> 27:06.070
Then,

27:06.190 --> 27:07.230
in exchange,

27:07.470 --> 27:08.310
Miss He,

27:08.500 --> 27:09.740
can you let me keep

27:09.870 --> 27:10.950
this wondrous memory?

27:13.230 --> 27:14.070
What?

27:14.190 --> 27:15.740
Do I need to re-introduce myself?

27:18.340 --> 27:19.540
I'm Duan Xu,

27:20.300 --> 27:21.470
D-U-A-N, X-U.

27:22.630 --> 27:23.470
Style name, Shunxi.

27:24.230 --> 27:25.190
So, My Lady,

27:25.740 --> 27:26.820
who are you?

27:28.580 --> 27:29.780
By night, I carry a lantern

27:30.740 --> 27:31.910
to guide mortals.

27:32.820 --> 27:34.190
By day, I carry a lantern

27:35.020 --> 27:36.470
to guide spirits.

27:38.390 --> 27:39.670
I am

27:40.630 --> 27:41.950
the Sovereign of Spirits.

27:49.780 --> 27:50.630
According to legend,

27:52.870 --> 27:54.020
at the end of the East Sea

27:55.630 --> 27:56.950
is Fusang Tree.

27:57.950 --> 28:00.100
Under the tree is the Void Spirit World,

28:00.100 --> 28:01.230
governed by the Sovereign.

28:02.670 --> 28:03.540
I thought

28:03.910 --> 28:04.910
it was just a fabrication

28:04.910 --> 28:05.820
from fascinating books.

28:06.150 --> 28:07.540
So, it really exists.

28:08.910 --> 28:09.870
If I have the chance,

28:10.820 --> 28:12.100
I want to visit the Spirit World.

28:12.950 --> 28:14.060
For centuries,

28:14.500 --> 28:16.300
some information from the Spirit World

28:16.300 --> 28:17.580
has reached the Mortal World.

28:18.150 --> 28:20.020
But the world is way too vast.

28:22.710 --> 28:24.100
Where can be considered

28:24.100 --> 28:25.100
the end of the East Sea?

28:26.190 --> 28:27.190
Just by this alone,

28:28.020 --> 28:29.390
mortals can't make it

28:29.390 --> 28:30.390
into the Spirit World.

28:31.580 --> 28:32.580
Obviously,

28:33.260 --> 28:34.910
I'm not He Xiaoxiao.

28:35.990 --> 28:37.430
And you're not Duan Xu.

28:40.990 --> 28:42.430
What are you talking about?

28:43.500 --> 28:44.470
I am Duan Xu.

28:44.990 --> 28:46.630
And my style name is Shunxi.

28:47.150 --> 28:48.190
My grandpa and my father

28:48.470 --> 28:49.340
chose the names.

28:50.230 --> 28:51.100
I'm genuine.

28:51.390 --> 28:52.390
Don't try to fool me.

28:57.470 --> 28:58.500
Listen.

28:59.190 --> 29:00.470
I'm here to save you

29:00.820 --> 29:01.670
because I want

29:01.670 --> 29:02.950
to make a deal with you.

29:03.990 --> 29:05.340
What an honor to make a deal

29:06.630 --> 29:07.780
with you, Your Grace.

29:09.260 --> 29:10.100
But sadly,

29:11.190 --> 29:12.030
I'm...

29:14.470 --> 29:15.430
Let's not stay here.

29:16.100 --> 29:17.540
Shall we talk about it

29:18.020 --> 29:18.860
back in Shuozhou?

29:19.540 --> 29:21.470
You're procrastinating.

29:22.060 --> 29:23.060
How do you know

29:23.870 --> 29:24.910
I'm not begging you?

29:26.260 --> 29:27.780
People don't usually beg

29:28.230 --> 29:29.390
with this tough attitude.

29:37.780 --> 29:38.620
Your Grace,

29:39.300 --> 29:40.630
I'll be waiting for you

29:41.060 --> 29:42.060
in Shuozhou.

29:49.470 --> 29:50.310
What happened?

29:50.540 --> 29:51.380
Where's our enemy?

29:51.400 --> 29:52.240
Where are they?

29:52.260 --> 29:53.340
Yeah. Where are they?

29:54.060 --> 29:55.300
They must have been driven off.

29:55.780 --> 29:56.740
Clear the battlefield.

29:56.740 --> 29:57.580
- Hurry.
- Yeah.

29:58.340 --> 29:59.870
Let's take back the weapons.

29:59.870 --> 30:00.710
- Yes.
- Yes.

30:08.990 --> 30:09.830
General.

30:10.710 --> 30:11.550
I'm sorry

30:11.550 --> 30:12.420
for that.

30:15.990 --> 30:17.430
I think the two of us

30:18.020 --> 30:19.500
can't avoid fighting with swords.

30:19.870 --> 30:20.710
In that situation,

30:21.060 --> 30:21.900
I was too nervous.

30:22.630 --> 30:23.470
Please forgive me.

30:27.500 --> 30:28.340
Xiaoxiao.

30:29.150 --> 30:29.990
Xiaoxiao.

30:31.150 --> 30:31.990
Xiao...

30:35.470 --> 30:36.820
She's a real sleepyhead.

30:43.230 --> 30:44.430
Where's her jade pendant?

31:04.100 --> 31:04.940
I knew it.

31:06.390 --> 31:08.540
He Simu's spirit has left this body.

31:09.500 --> 31:11.540
Once I know who this girl is,

31:12.190 --> 31:13.540
I will know

31:13.540 --> 31:14.990
how to restrain He Simu.

31:30.870 --> 31:31.710
General,

31:31.950 --> 31:33.260
you're finally back.

31:37.340 --> 31:38.190
Commandant Wu,

31:39.150 --> 31:40.470
I finally made it back alive

31:40.470 --> 31:41.310
after much hardship.

31:41.540 --> 31:42.380
Yes, yes.

31:42.540 --> 31:43.380
General,

31:43.500 --> 31:44.390
when you're back,

31:44.710 --> 31:45.780
I'll have to return

31:45.990 --> 31:46.870
the military command

31:47.230 --> 31:48.070
to you.

31:48.780 --> 31:49.910
You should be happy.

31:53.710 --> 31:54.550
General.

31:55.300 --> 31:56.140
Thank you.

31:57.740 --> 31:58.910
Thank you

32:00.630 --> 32:02.190
for doing that for people in Shuozhou

32:03.230 --> 32:04.150
as well as me.

32:06.680 --> 32:07.520
General,

32:07.540 --> 32:08.380
you're injured?

32:08.820 --> 32:09.660
I'm fine.

32:09.820 --> 32:10.660
Commandant Wu.

32:11.230 --> 32:12.670
Handle these supplies properly.

32:13.190 --> 32:14.340
No more lapses.

32:15.060 --> 32:16.430
Count on me, General.

32:16.870 --> 32:18.100
These supplies

32:18.260 --> 32:19.950
will last over half a month.

32:31.260 --> 32:32.710
Han Lingqiu is accused of treason.

32:33.390 --> 32:34.260
He'll be detained now

32:34.820 --> 32:35.660
and punished later.

32:36.300 --> 32:37.140
General,

32:37.390 --> 32:38.230
what's going on here?

32:38.540 --> 32:39.820
Someone sold our secrets.

32:40.670 --> 32:41.670
During the grain raid,

32:41.870 --> 32:43.190
Chong troops ambushed us.

32:43.710 --> 32:44.950
We nearly got wiped out.

32:45.820 --> 32:46.670
Then how do you know

32:46.670 --> 32:47.630
it was Han?

32:47.990 --> 32:48.910
Because besides me,

32:50.470 --> 32:51.310
he was the only man

32:52.780 --> 32:54.540
Chong troops wanted to take alive.

32:57.390 --> 32:58.400
- Move.
- Move.

32:59.150 --> 32:59.990
But...

33:08.950 --> 33:09.950
Xiaoxiao, you're awake.

33:14.300 --> 33:15.820
When I was asleep,

33:16.100 --> 33:17.260
did anyone come in?

33:17.810 --> 33:18.650
No.

33:18.670 --> 33:19.510
What's wrong?

33:31.100 --> 33:32.670
Her jade pendant is back.

33:36.260 --> 33:37.780
Did I see wrong?

33:40.580 --> 33:42.190
Let's make a deal.

33:43.100 --> 33:44.470
I'm all ears.

33:45.440 --> 33:46.300
I'll fulfill

33:46.300 --> 33:47.390
one of your wishes.

33:47.910 --> 33:48.990
In exchange,

33:49.470 --> 33:51.230
you'll lend me one of your five senses.

33:52.470 --> 33:53.540
One wish

33:53.990 --> 33:54.990
for one sense.

33:56.820 --> 33:57.670
For ten days.

33:59.910 --> 34:01.150
What if I refuse?

34:11.100 --> 34:12.430
Under such circumstances,

34:12.910 --> 34:14.500
you don't get a say.

34:24.321 --> 34:29.651
♪Between black and white,
ripples crossed♪

34:29.981 --> 34:34.231
♪Light encountered shadow♪

34:35.591 --> 34:40.961
♪It pierced the darkness and the time♪

34:41.261 --> 34:45.861
♪The unbreakable fate♪

34:46.951 --> 34:48.791
♪Suddenly cracked♪

35:01.001 --> 35:06.441
♪Between black and white,
ripples crossed♪

35:06.621 --> 35:10.951
♪Light encountered shadow♪

35:12.321 --> 35:17.711
♪It pierced the darkness and the time♪

35:17.941 --> 35:21.881
♪The unbreakable fate♪

35:23.651 --> 35:25.541
♪Suddenly cracked♪

35:28.201 --> 35:31.361
♪Listen, all sounds are roaring♪

35:31.361 --> 35:33.891
♪As cold ice turns into tides♪

35:33.891 --> 35:39.411
♪A century's loneliness melts dreams♪

35:39.411 --> 35:42.651
♪Following fate's guidance♪

35:42.651 --> 35:47.511
♪By fate, our moments were exchanged♪

35:47.851 --> 35:50.871
♪The heart wakes up all of a sudden♪

35:50.871 --> 35:53.691
♪Watch fireworks fall like stars♪

35:53.951 --> 35:56.481
♪This bond is tangled into a thread♪

35:56.481 --> 36:01.901
♪Worldly reflections fade into mist♪

36:02.071 --> 36:05.141
♪Borrowing one fleeting heartbeat♪

36:05.301 --> 36:10.201
♪You drew me into mortal dust,
till I'm enamored with its charms♪

36:10.411 --> 36:13.881
♪The heart wakes up all of a sudden♪
